  m_text: '================ Main ===============


    We are playing as Tarjo Prakoso,
    a literate sawit farmer that use automation to do his bussines. Instead of manually
    farm the land, he instead use drone that he controlled from he''s computer to
    farm. So instead of doing by hand Tarjo Prakoso type a command on a command line
    interface to manage his land.'
